### Get all users
GET https://localhost:5280/api/users
Accept: application/json

### Get user by ID
GET https://localhost:5280/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

### Create a new user
POST https://localhost:5280/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Grace",
  "lastName": "Hopper",
  "email": "grace@example.com",
  "isActive": true
}

### Update an existing user
PUT https://localhost:5280/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "firstName": "Ada",
  "lastName": "Lovelace",
  "email": "ada.l@example.com",
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete a user
DELETE https://localhost:5280/api/users/1
Accept: application/json
